In 2012, during the GlobalVoices Summit in Nairobi, Rising Voices
[partnered](https://rising.globalvoicesonline.org/blog/2012/07/07/citizen-
journalism-partnership-with-map-kibera-during-gv-summit/) with Map Kibera
Trust and Kibera News Network to bring together members of the Global Voices
community and groups in Kibera to share experiences and to participate in a
joint citizen journalism activity.

